wnship, Ohio...", "last_comment_created": 1783050061089, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 10, "score_up": 216, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "\u262a\ufe0f\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u262a\ufe0f", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlu07c5", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 40, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8711185, "raw_content": "", "author": "MADASHELLNEWS", "created": 1783076818815, "profile_picture": "he2bJfDz7cL8", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "BillGateCanSuckIt", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.alexjoneslive.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.alexjoneslive.com/2026/07/02/cops-bust-transgender-with-massive-cache-of-firearms-before-casino-shooting-rampage/", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Cops Bust Transgender with Massive Cache of Firearms Before Casino Shooting Rampage", "last_comment_created": 1783080392756, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 40, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "Las Vegas police received 911 call from trans' ex warning he stole vehicle, planned to commit 'suicide by cop.'", "large_image": "vaS46b7Bx2wXL05R.png", "title": "Cops Bust Transgender with Massive Cache of Firearms Before Casino Shooting Rampage - Alex Jones Live"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBlu0fmC", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 24, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8711390, "raw_content": "Cliff notes version: \n\nThere's a refuge (Parker River National Wildlife Refuge) that has impoundments protecting it from nearby salt water, the impoundments are created by a series of earthen dikes.  MILLIONS of birds use it every year for a stop-over in migration.   People within the previous administration, who are still in charge of this area, decided that in a century, climate change may have caused sea levels to rise and the dikes could be breached, and cause a catastrophic failure.  So the logical decision is to blow up the dikes and flood the area with salt water. I'm not joking.  Once that happens, the habitat that is being used by those millions of birds, many of them endangered, will be destroyed.   The plan was justified because it would potentially benefit a single species, the saltmarsh sparrow.  This would create maybe an extra 2% addition to the habitat for the sparrow, and it would be D-grade habitat.  \n\nI love this refuge, and there is not a single person that goes there that is on board with this plan.  It's horrendous; \"climate change\" might impact things almost a century from now, so let's destroy it today.   The 'independent study' was basically a rubber-stamp process, and the public's input was largely ignored. \n\nI don't know where else to turn, if anyone here has an \"in\" with Burgum's office, or a way to get this to someone in his office, please DM me.  I have a much longer version of what is happening, and why it's insane, but I wanted to make a brief post here in begging for help.  ", "author": "AccipiterQQ", "created": 1783087511198, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Captntrouble", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Can anyone help me get in touch with Doug Burgum's office? I have an urgent matter.  The federal government is about to destroy a national wildlife refuge near me because climate change might destroy it 80 years from now.  I'm not joking. ", "last_comment_created": 1783089446466, "content": "<p>Cliff notes version:</p>\n<p>There's a refuge (Parker River National Wildlife Refuge) that has impoundments protecting it from nearby salt water, the impoundments are created by a series of earthen dikes.  MILLIONS of birds use it every year for a stop-over in migration.   People within the previous administration, who are still in charge of this area, decided that in a century, climate change may have caused sea levels to rise and the dikes could be breached, and cause a catastrophic failure.  So the logical decision is to blow up the dikes and flood the area with salt water. I'm not joking.  Once that happens, the habitat that is being used by those millions of birds, many of them endangered, will be destroyed.   The plan was justified because it would potentially benefit a single species, the saltmarsh sparrow.  This would create maybe an extra 2% addition to the habitat for the sparrow, and it would be D-grade habitat.</p>\n<p>I love this refuge, and there is not a single person that goes there that is on board with this plan.  It's horrendous; &quot;climate change&quot; might impact things almost a century from now, so let's destroy it today.   The 'independent study' was basically a rubber-stamp process, and the public's input was largely ignored.</p>\n<p>I don't know where else to turn, if anyone here has an &quot;in&quot; with Burgum's office, or a way to get this to someone in his office, please DM me.  I have a much longer version of what is happening, and why it's insane, but I wanted to make a brief post here in begging for help.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 24, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlu0wQX", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 21, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8711435, "raw_content": "", "author": "MakinBacon", "created": 1783089281435, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DeadOverRed", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.jpost.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBlu0wQX.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.jpost.com/international/article-899158", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "So israel was interfering in elections?!?! ", "last_comment_created": 1783095368628, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 29, "score_up": 21, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "Last month, Reuters reported that French authorities suspected BlackCore was behind an online smear campaign targeting three candidates from the hard-left France Unbowed party (LFI).", "large_image": "XQzNHN2NEgGTgcsc.png", "title": "Israeli firm BlackCore suspecte